articles.title: The billionaire who fueled JD Vance's rapid rise to the Trump VP spot — analysis - CBS News
articles.description: Vance's most prominent benefactor over the years has been iconoclastic tech investor Peter Thiel, who in recent months said he's not giving money to any politician in 2024.
